data.description: STUNNING, one of a kind home, located in quiet Sandy neighborhood near Jordan River Trail. Extraordinary remodel throughout, resembling the PERSONALITY and QUALITY of the HIGHEST END HOMES. Impressive design and gorgeous details in every corner that captivate and intrigue. Over $230,000 INVESTED to create this masterpiece. Included in remodel are new kitchen cabinets, smart appliances, quartz countertops, flooring, lighting, front door, plantation shutters, paint inside and out, furnace, garage door and floor, sinks, faucets,  deck, full landscaping, sprinklers, fence, deck, pergola, hot tub and so, so much more (full list attached to listing). Easy to care for yard that offers privacy and INCREDIBLE BEAUTY at every turn. BRAND NEW HOT TUB INCLUDED. Easy access to I-15, Trax and shopping. You will not be disappointed. Make appointment to see now!
